            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>警惕！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E8%84%91%E5%8D%92%E4%B8%AD%E5%89%8D%E5%85%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E8%84%91%E5%8D%92%E4%B8%AD%E5%89%8D%E5%85%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#出现这些情况可能是脑卒中前兆#</span></a>】脑卒中俗称“中风”。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E6%AF%8F5%E4%BD%8D%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85%E4%B8%AD%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%911%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%AD%E9%A3%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E6%AF%8F5%E4%BD%8D%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85%E4%B8%AD%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%911%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%AD%E9%A3%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#在我国每5位死者中至少1人死于中风#</span></a>，带病生存的脑卒中患者达1300万人，且发病人群呈年轻化。①突然口齿不清②突发头晕、头痛③视物不清④偏瘫⑤呕吐⑥过度嗜睡，这些都可能是脑卒中的预警信号！如何预防脑卒中？遇到突发脑卒中如何急救？戳👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjbw7rhpu2j20u01iy7hw.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjbw7r9xr9j20u01if4a2.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjbw7skclaj20u02dxh2n.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjbw7soe7oj20u028c4fh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjbw7lxwp9j20u00u0gsh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjbw7si4kvj20u028ch1o.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjbw7rv0lfj20u01ydtnp.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjbw7tav25j20u024x4gd.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjbw7rcs3ej20u020znap.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
